<p>A <code>FiveStarRatingPickerButton</code> is one star inside
  a <a href="/components/five-star-rating-picker/"><code>FiveStarRatingPicker</code></a>.
  Each button is a <code>&lt;button role="radio"&gt;</code> with
  <code>data-value</code> (1–5) and an auto-generated aria-label
  like "Rate 4 stars".</p>

<p>See the <a href="/components/five-star-rating-picker/">Picker
  demo</a> for composed examples.</p>
